<doc id="995037" wikidata="Q4717937" url="?curid=995037" title="Aleck W. McAllister">
<text>Aleck Winter &quot;Alex&quot; McAllister (1887–1956) was an American politician who holds the record as the longest-serving mayor of Huntsville, Alabama, having served for 26 years, from 1926 to 1952. He is buried at Maple Hill Cemetery in Huntsville.

