* Gustave Reese, &quot;Music in the Renaissance&quot;. New York, W.W. Norton &amp; Co., 1954. 
* Article &quot;Alonso Lobo&quot; in &quot;The New Grove Dictionary of Music and Musicians&quot;, ed. Stanley Sadie. 20 vol. London, Macmillan Publishers Ltd., 1980. 

