====II. Nonsymmetric Case====
Next we consider the case where the system does not have a symmetry. In this case there is no reason to keep only even powers of formula_1 in the expansion of formula_46, and a cubic term must be allowed (The linear term can always be eliminated by a shift formula_99 + constant.) We thus consider a free energy functional

